OL,4,Csentenced over historic abuse at
OL,5,Cchildren's homes
OL,7,FA former nun who assaulted vulnerable
OL,8,Fyoung people at children's homes more
OL,9,Fthan 40 years ago has been jailed.
OL,11,FNun Carol Buirds, 75, known as Sister
OL,12,FCarmel Rose, was jailed for 15 months
OL,13,Fafter being found guilty of 13 charges
OL,14,Fincluding assault to severe injury,
OL,15,Fthe Crown Office said.
