OL,3,CFormer nuns and support worker
OL,4,Csentenced over historic abuse at
OL,5,Cchildren's homes
OL,7,FShe locked one child in a cupboard and
OL,8,Fanother in an unlit cellar without
OL,9,Faccess to water, and was found to have
OL,10,Frepeatedly assaulted children, often
OL,11,Fusing implements such as a belt, a
OL,12,Fwooden ruler, and a stick, prosecutors
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FAnother former nun and a retired
OL,16,Fsupport worker were also sentenced at
OL,17,FEdinburgh Sheriff Court on Thursday 15
OL,18,FJanuary.
