OL,7,FEileen McElhinney, 78, who was known
OL,8,Fas Sister Mary Eileen, as well as ex-
OL,9,Fsupport worker Dorothy Kane, 68, were
OL,10,Ffound guilty of subjecting multiple
OL,11,Fvictims to cruel and unnatural
OL,12,Ftreatment over nine years.
OL,14,FThe victims, who are all now adults,
OL,15,Fwere aged between five and 14 when the
OL,16,Fabuse began. Witnesses for the
OL,17,Fprosecution included former residents,
OL,18,Fan ex-staff member and a social worker.
