OL,7,FSupport worker Kane said she "couldn't
OL,8,Fremember", in a police interview
OL,9,Frecorded on video which was released
OL,10,Fby the Crown Office after sentencing.
OL,11,FShe denied knowing children had been
OL,12,Fstruck with an implement, and said
OL,13,F"No" when asked if she considered them
OL,14,Fto be appropriate, adding she "would
OL,15,Fhave intervened" if she had seen a
OL,16,Fpunishment.
