OL,7,FMcElhinney was found guilty of five
OL,8,Fcharges, including violently
OL,9,Fassaulting young children. She also
OL,10,Fforced them to stand in cold showers
OL,11,Fand sit in cold baths, and used a
OL,12,Fhairbrush to hit one child on the
OL,13,Fbuttocks, prosecutors said.
OL,15,FThe former nun hurt another boy with a
OL,16,Fmetal comb, refusing to stop brushing
OL,17,Fhis hair despite him being in pain.
