OL,7,FKane was found guilty of two charges
OL,8,Fof cruel and unnatural treatment for
OL,9,Frepeatedly grabbing a boy, including
OL,10,Fby the hair, and restraining him by
OL,11,Fforcing her knees on to his chest. She
OL,12,Falso failed to intervene when
OL,13,Fwitnessing another member of staff
OL,14,Fassaulting the child, and forced a
OL,15,Fsecond young person into a cupboard
OL,16,Fbefore locking him in.
