OL,3,CFormer nuns and support worker
OL,4,Csentenced over historic abuse at
OL,5,Cchildren's homes
OL,7,F"Although these offences took place
OL,8,Fdecades ago, such abuse has never been
OL,9,Facceptable and should never have
OL,10,Fhappened.
OL,12,F"The charge of cruel and unnatural
OL,13,Ftreatment reflects the sustained and
OL,14,Fsystematic nature of this abuse over
OL,15,Fan extended period.
OL,17,F"Scotland's prosecutors remain fully
OL,18,Fcommitted to bringing non-recent child
OL,19,Fabuse cases before the courts, no
OL,20,Fmatter how much time has passed since
OL,21,Fthese crimes were committed."
